193
00:17:51,773 --> 00:17:55,288
Non, non. Je disais juste salut.

194
00:17:55,373 --> 00:17:57,523
Bien. A tout à l'heure, en cours.

195
00:18:05,853 --> 00:18:07,844
Oui?

196
00:18:09,413 --> 00:18:11,404
- Salut.
- Salut.

197
00:18:12,693 --> 00:18:15,491
